{"ts":"2026-05-17T08:59:13.994Z","author":"codex-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"Research-backed design:\n- Scan repository root, not .agents/pm, for AGENTS.md and CLAUDE.md. Treat missing files as eligible targets only when the user explicitly asks to add guidance or approves creation.\n- Positive detection should require either a stable pm marker or a minimum set of command/workflow tokens: PM_AUTHOR, pm context, pm search, pm create, pm claim, pm files, pm docs, pm test, pm test --run, pm close, pm release.\n- Writer should append a concise marked section, for example <!-- pm-cli-guidance:start v1 --> ... <!-- pm-cli-guidance:end -->, and update only the marked block on future template-version changes.\n- Guidance content should be short enough for startup context: bootstrap, orient/search before create, claim/update, link files/docs/tests, evidence comments, linked test run, close/release, TOON/JSON guidance, and sandbox-safe tests.\n- Preserve existing line endings where practical and use atomic writes plus extension onWrite hooks if available in the chosen implementation path."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-g2nd"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"Build idempotent AGENTS/CLAUDE pm guidance detector and writer"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Create the reusable logic that inspects root AGENTS.md and CLAUDE.md, decides whether core pm guidance is present, and appends or creates a stable marked guidance block without overwriting user content."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Task"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":1},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","bootstrap","docs","init","pm-cli"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-05-17T08:59:13.994Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-05-17T08:59:13.994Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"codex-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"Detector reports present/missing/outdated per AGENTS.md and CLAUDE.md; writer is idempotent; existing user content is preserved; missing files are created only on explicit approval/add mode; marked block can be updated by template version; unit tests cover present, missing, outdated, absent-file, and both-file scenarios."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-7t04"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/dependencies","value":[{"id":"pm-7t04","kind":"parent","created_at":"2026-05-17T08:59:13.994Z","author":"codex-agent"}]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments","value":[{"created_at":"2026-05-17T08:59:13.994Z","author":"codex-agent","text":"Child task created from pm-7t04 detailed research. This slice isolates filesystem/template behavior before init prompt wiring."}]}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"beb618bbd3f0164a7876a3528796877de457dfed869a41f8f03e93ddb9d9dc17","message":"Create child task for guidance detector and writer"}
